title: Corrosion Of Conformity - Westwood One (Deluxe 2-CD) 2017 ak
description:
Corrosion Of Conformity - Westwood One (Deluxe 2-CD) 2017 ak

A project I made awhile back but I was motovated to Deluxe it. 
Did I say that I like this band and Southern Sludge?
Anyway as we wait for the NEW album from these guys lets get in the right frame of mind.
